    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2011-02-17</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2011-02-22T20:05:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Phylicia's Law - Requires each local educational agency (LEA) that receives funds under the Safe and Drug-Free Schools and Communities program to develop and make publicly available a written school safety policy for off-premises, overnight field trips.</p> <p>Encourages the Secretary of Education to provide guidance to such LEAs by taking the steps necessary, such as hosting a conference of interested parties, to further the development of a model school safety policy for such trips.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
